column5: Looking for some areas to hunt down some fish but only have the coordinates for the areas.. Could anyone help me as to how to put these into google maps?
How to put Long/Lat Coordinates into google maps  Type the title of your quest into google, instructions are there.
Figured it out, was having some technical difficulties and all of the areas that I wanted were apperently in china! Haha all figured out now though
Needless to say you could probably post all the co-ords in red here, I don't think anyone is going to go and swipe your secret spots.  Not after they show you how they fish farm over there.

Check to ensure the map datums are the same in your gps as they are in google maps.  I dont know how to check this, but i would assume google uses WGS 84.  You could be off by hundreds of meters if they are different!
